ing: 1 (3.4 ounce) package instant pistachio pudding mix
1 (8 ounce) can crushed pineapple, with juice
1/2 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "This chilly delight is an American classic."
ins: In a large bowl, mix together pudding mix, pineapple with juice, marshmallows, and nuts. Fold in whipped topping. Chill.
